00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:21,720
the director really likes you.

289
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,200
Not bad, kid.

290
00:14:24,160 --> 00:14:25,960
You actually have some acting chops.

291
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,480
What do you mean?

292
00:14:28,880 --> 00:14:30,400
So, you were looking down on me, weren't you?

293
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:31,640
I wasn't.

294
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:33,440
I just used to think

295
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:36,080
that you only had one way of acting.

296
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:38,040
By the way

297
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:40,080
that music project from the company

298
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,200
have you decided yet?

299
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:42,440
I'm not doing it.

300
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:43,920
Don't be like that.

301
00:14:44,040 --> 00:14:45,280
It's a fan economy now.

302
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:47,080
Your fans would definitely love to hear you sing.

303
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:48,520
Brother

304
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:50,480
I'm tone-deaf.

305
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,000
What was the company thinking

306
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,000
asking me to release a single?

307
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:55,320
Don't worry about that.

308
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,160
They can fix everything in the recording studio.

309
00:14:57,520 --> 00:14:58,360
I'm not willing to do it.

310
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:00,920
I know exactly

311
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:02,320
what I'm good at.

312
00:15:02,880 --> 00:15:04,320
I can't just take any kind of money.

313
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:05,520
I think

314
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:07,160
being like Jian Mo is actually quite good.

315
00:15:07,880 --> 00:15:09,280
Doing what you love...

316
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:10,720
focused and serious.

317
00:15:11,400 --> 00:15:12,080
Him?

318
00:15:12,520 --> 00:15:13,760
If he doesn't become a bit more flexible...

319
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:15,680
he won't be able to make a living as an actor much longer.

320
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:18,880
What do you mean?

321
00:15:19,560 --> 00:15:20,480
You don't know yet?

322
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:21,760
For our drama

323
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:24,080
they might not even choose him as the lead.

324
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:34,840
Hello, Director. I'm Jian Mo.

325
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:36,200
The following is my audition.

326
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:41,200
Hello, Director.

327
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:42,120
I'm Jian Mo.

328
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:43,120
The following is my audition.

329
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:45,320
Fantasizing as the Dragon-Slaying Warrior

330
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:46,480
who can lead the charge

331
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:47,360
Hello, Director.

332
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:48,280
I'm Jian Mo.

333
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:49,480
The following is my audition.

334
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:51,600
Thank you.

335
00:15:55,680 --> 00:15:56,320
Wu Jie.

336
00:15:57,040 --> 00:15:58,120
I've sent you three audition clips today.

337
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:58,920
Please take a look.

338
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:00,160
Have a look at them.

339
00:16:01,040 --> 00:16:01,560
By the way

340
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:03,640
how is Director An's project going?

341
00:16:04,040 --> 00:16:04,960
Have they decided?

342
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,560
I was just about to tell you.

343
00:16:12,560 --> 00:16:14,640
Director An chose Hu Sinan for that role.

344
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,080
What about the platform project?

345
00:16:20,040 --> 00:16:21,400
They also politely declined us.

346
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:23,240
Then

347
00:16:23,560 --> 00:16:24,120
None?

348
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:26,560
There's no news from any of the current auditions.

349
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:28,520
If there is, I'll let you know.

350
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:30,480
Jian Mo.

351
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:31,760
Are you okay?

352
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:32,960
Don't overthink it.

353
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:33,640
You...

354
00:16:34,040 --> 00:16:34,560
Oh, right.

355
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:36,720
I just remembered

356
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:40,360
there's a graduate student filming a thesis project.

357
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:41,920
Help me contact them.

358
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:43,160
I'm willing to do it.

359
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:44,040
A？

360
00:16:44,400 --> 00:16:45,400
A student project?

361
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:46,880
The pay will definitely be very low.

362
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:47,920
So what?

363
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:49,960
My expenses aren't high anyway.

364
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:51,920
As long as I can support myself, it's fine.

365
00:16:52,160 --> 00:16:53,040
Mainly

366
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:55,240
it’s about being able to film more.

367
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:58,440
Alright, I'll contact them for you.

368
00:16:58,720 --> 00:16:59,320
By the way

369
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:01,600
The results of the Qilu project are ou

370
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:05,480
What did they say?

371
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,800
Xu Xinglang! Look here!

372
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:27,000
Why are you performing in a same-sex themed project?

373
00:17:27,280 --> 00:17:28,520
How is your working relationship

374
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:30,040
Do you contact each other often in private

375
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:34,120
It looks like these filming days won't be peaceful.

376
00:17:34,600 --> 00:17:36,280
I know you like peace and quiet.

377
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:38,240
I’m afraid you'll just have to bear it.

378
00:17:40,040 --> 00:17:41,120
I'm already very grateful

379
00:17:41,120 --> 00:17:42,480
the director fought to keep me in the cast.

380
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:43,680
This is nothing.

381
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:45,560
It’s not like I’m some inexperienced newcomer.

382
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:46,200
True.

383
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,280
I'll just avoid them.

384
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:48,840
They’re all here to interview Xu Xinglang.

385
00:17:48,840 --> 00:17:49,960
It has nothing to do with us.

386
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:52,880
It’s Jian Mo!

387
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,520
Jian Mo

388
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:02,200
Teacher Jian Mo, you’re filming with Xu Xinglang

389
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:03,440
how is your private relationship?

390
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:05,360
This project is same-sex themed

391
00:18:05,520 --> 00:18:06,520
will you develop feelings for him?

392
00:18:06,760 --> 00:18:07,920
Could you tell us

393
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:10,240
It's not convenient for us right now

394
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:11,640
Let's schedule separately later

395
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:13,440
It's not convenient to answer now

396
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:20,800
Let me through, please.

397
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:22,000
Thank you.

398
00:18:36,080 --> 00:18:36,920
Teacher Jian.

399
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:40,200
I didn't expect you to be so popular.

400
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:41,480
What didn't you expect?

401
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:43,640
Aren't those all your fans out there?

402
00:18:45,360 --> 00:18:46,200
Put it this way...

403
00:18:46,560 --> 00:18:47,680
are you saying you’re riding on my fame?

404
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:49,760
Riding on your fame?

405
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:51,280
Please.

406
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:53,680
What kind of ridiculous questions were those?

407
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:55,080
Asking

408
00:18:55,760 --> 00:18:58,080
if I would develop feelings for you.

409
00:18:58,960 --> 00:19:00,040
How ridiculous.

410
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:03,880
What are you recording?

411
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:06,280
We’re filming a "joining the cast" vlog.

412
00:19:06,840 --> 00:19:08,200
I captured this part beautifully.

413
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:09,640
Thanks.

414
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:11,760
For providing us with such valuable material.

415
00:19:15,760 --> 00:19:17,400
Let's go. The elevator is over there.

416
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:23,920
Teacher Jian, won't you join us?

417
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:27,080
The reporters are all outside.

418
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:28,720
Do you want them to photograph you?

419
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:53,280
It seems you'll have to get used to this.

420
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:56,960
This kind of thing will only increase, not decrease.

421
00:19:57,840 --> 00:19:59,160
We have a long way to go together.

422
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:02,320
Don't cause me trouble.

423
00:20:05,520 --> 00:20:06,680
I can't guarantee that.

424
00:20:07,520 --> 00:20:08,680
You’ve never been famous

425
00:20:09,040 --> 00:20:10,840
so naturally, you don't know my troubles.
